In re Seavolt.

[Cite as In re Seavolt, 121 Ohio St.3d 269, 2009-Ohio-1061.]

(No. 2007-1258 — Submitted January 21, 2009 — 2009.) Timothy Young, Ohio Public Defender, and Molly J. Bruns, Assistant State Public Defender, for appellant, Tracy Seavolt.

{¶ 1} The judgment of the court of appeals is affirmed on the authority of State v. D.H., 120 Ohio St.3d 540, 2009-Ohio-9, 901 N.E.2d 209.

Moyer, C.J., and Pfeifer, Lundberg Stratton, O’Connor, O’Donnell, Lanzinger, and Cupp, JJ., concur.
